I've been using the fantastic program ddccontrol for a while, and it 
works with my monitor without problems, but it tells me my monitor is 
not in the database, so I wanted to give you the output of the probing 
command.

My monitor is a Hannspree HQ272. The installed database version (I'm on 
Manjaro Linux and got it out of the AUR) is 
ddccontrol-db-git-20210113.rdd19622-1

Hope this info is useful to you! And a big thank you for developing this 
great program :)

Best regards
Andreas



